      <body>
         <div>
            <head>"DREAM VARIATION"</head>
            <lg>
               <l>To <rs type="actionWords">fling</rs> my arms <rs type="rhymeA"><rs type="enjambment">wide</rs></rs> <rs type="printingError">7</rs></l>
               <l>In some place of the <rs type="rhymeB">sun<rs type="endstop">,</rs></rs></l>
               <l>To <rs type="actionWords">whirl</rs> and to <rs type="rhymeC"><rs type="enjambment">dance</rs></rs></l>
               <l>Till the bright day is <rs type="rhymeB">done</rs><rs type='endstop'>.</rs></l>
               <l>Then rest at cool <rs type="rhymeD"><rs type="enjambment">evening</rs></rs></l>
               <l>Beneath a tall <rs type="rhymeE"><rs type="enjambment">tree</rs></rs></l>
               <l>While night comes <rs type="rhymeE"><rs type="enjambment">gently</rs></rs></l>
               <l>Dark <rs type="simile">like</rs> <rs type="rhymeE">me</rs><rs type="endstop">.</rs></l>
               <l><rs type="theme:blackJoyAndYearningForFreedom">That is my <rs type="rhymeF">dream<rs type="endstop">.</rs></rs></rs></l>
               <l>To <rs type="actionWords">fling</rs> my arms <rs type="rhymeA"><rs type="enjambment">wide</rs></rs></l>
               <l>In the face of the <rs type="rhymeB">sun</rs><rs type="endstop">.</rs></l>
               <l><rs type="actionWords">Dance! Whirl! <rs type="rhymeG">Whirl<rs type="endstop">!</rs></rs></rs></l>
               <l>Till the quick day is <rs type="rhymeB">done<rs type="endstop">.</rs></rs></l>
               <l>Rest at pale <rs type="rhymeD">evening<rs type="endstop">,</rs></rs></l>
               <l>A tall, slim <rs type="E">tree<rs type="endstop">,</rs></rs></l>
               <l>Night coming <rs type="rhymeE"><rs type="enjambment">tenderly</rs></rs></l>
               <l>Black <rs type="simile">like</rs> <rs type="rhymeE">me<rs type="endstop">.</rs></rs></l>
            </lg>
            <byline>-Langston Hughes</byline>
         </div>
